@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam defaultFontName Microsoft YaHei
title 任务执行流程与状态

skinparam component {
    BackgroundColor<<task>> LightBlue
    BackgroundColor<<memory>> LightGreen
    BackgroundColor<<decision>> LightYellow
}

component "任务队列" as TQ <<task>>
component "执行中" as Running <<task>>
component "等待 Claude" as Waiting <<task>>
component "处理结果" as Processing <<task>>
component "任务完成" as Done <<task>>

component "记忆系统" as Memory <<memory>>
component "加载上下文" as Load <<memory>>
component "保存记忆" as Save <<memory>>
component "压缩检查" as Compress <<memory>>

TQ --> Running : get_next_task()
Running --> Waiting : invoke()
Waiting --> Processing : Claude 返回

Processing --> Running : 提取结果
Processing --> Done : should_continue()=False
Processing --> TQ : should_continue()=True

Processing --> Save : 更新记忆
Save --> Compress : 检查大小
Compress --> Load : 大小正常
Compress --> Memory : 压缩

Load --> Memory : 上下文就绪

note right of TQ
执行模式：
- 串行：Task1 → Task2 → Task3
- 并行：Task1, Task2, Task3 同时
end note

note right of Compress
压缩条件：
- session.md > 20000 字符
- context.md > 30000 字符
- knowledge > 25000 字符
end note

legend right
    |= 颜色 |= 类型 |
    |<#LightBlue>| 任务执行 |
    |<#LightGreen>| 记忆管理 |
endlegend

@enduml